Package: labscorer
Title: Psychometric Scale Scoring Pipeline for Research Labs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Lab", "Team", email = "lab@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A standardised pipeline for computing sum scores, mean scores, and
    subscale scores from psychometric questionnaire data. Supports automatic
    timepoint detection, item inversion, custom recoding, and built-in range
    validation via a diagnostic database. Designed so lab members can register
    new questionnaires by adding a single list entry.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
